data.description: This house is perfectly located, near Kennesaw State University and in a great school district, making it convenient and ideal for education. Say goodbye to dealing with any rules or fees from a homeowner association, so you have more freedom in your new home. You'll love the extra-long driveway, offering lots of parking space. When you step inside, you're greeted by a lovely foyer with a brand-new railing, giving you a taste of what the rest of the house is like. The sunroom lets in plenty of natural light and is a peaceful spot to enjoy the view of the fruit trees in the front yard. Plus, this house comes with the best siding, providing not just a beautiful exterior but also excellent durability. The backyard is perfect for hosting parties with a big concrete patio. It's surrounded by a fence for privacy and safety, making it great for gatherings or just relaxing under the stars. Inside, the house has been updated with new, easy-to-clean floors, so no more dealing with carpets. The basement is partially finished and has a full bathroom, giving you the chance to add another bedroom. You'll also have a big three-car garage for your vehicles and storage. Plus, the front patio has a special concrete block fountain that creates a calming atmosphere. Don't let this opportunity to make this your new home slip away!
